      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo obsoletes RFC 1514, the "Host Resources MIB".  This memo extends that specification by clarifying changes based on implementation and deployment experience and documenting the Host Resources MIB in SMIv2 format while remaining semantically identical to the existing SMIv1-based MIB. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
